All Implemented Interfaces:
Edge<UserProfile>
public class InteractionEdge extends EdgeImpl<UserProfile>
Represents an edge in a social network graph, specifically designed to handle interactions between user profiles. This class extends EdgeImpl to include social interaction types and dynamically calculates the weight.
